| statid | type | version | flags | c1   | c2   | c3   | c5   | n1   | n3   | ob_spec1 | ob_spec2 |
+--------+------+---------+-------+------+------+------+------+------+------+----------+----------+
| NULL   | T    |       8 |  NULL | T1   | NULL | NULL | TEST |  100 |   60 |        0 |        0 |
+--------+------+---------+-------+------+------+------+------+------+------+----------+----------+
